Package com.sirqul.sdk.api.games Description

Contains API classes that fall under the Games category. Includes AppDataApi, GameLevelApi, MissionApi, MissionInviteApi, PackApi, RankingApi, ScoreApi, ThemeDescriptorApi, and TicketApi.
